abstract: In leaked audio conversations with employees, the Facebook chief said he would take Ms. Warren to court if she tried to break up the company.

snippet: The proposal, which is in its early stages, would ratchet up tension ahead of trade talks next month.
lead_paragraph: WASHINGTON — The Trump administration is discussing whether to block Chinese companies from listing shares on American stock exchanges, the latest push to try to sever economic ties between the United States and China, according to people familiar with the deliberations.

abstract: Inwood has the lowest average rents in the borough. Now developers and their high-rise buildings are coming.
snippet: Inwood has the lowest average rents in the borough. Now developers and their high-rise buildings are coming.
lead_paragraph: For decades, Inwood has been one of New York City’s untouched gems. Nestled among rivers and rolling forest at the northernmost tip of Manhattan, the 500-acre neighborhood has again and again batted away the forces of gentrification — until now.
